Princess Diana caused a lot of controversy and scandal within the royal family when she was alive, but this one is by far the most outrageous!

Royal fans have been plagued by rumors that the late royal had a secret daughter before her death, and according to The GLOBE, Prince William and Prince Harry have a sister named Sarah Spencer!

After escaping a death plot on the island of Crete in June 2016, Sarah has been in hiding!

